ACAD_2_USE_BLOCK_LAYER_INFO "$(ACAD_IN_USE_BLOCK_LAYER_INFO_ACAD_2)"
GUI OPTIONAL CHECKBOX_WITHLABEL ACAD_IN_USE_BLOCK_LAYER_INFO_ACAD_2 yes%no Use Block Layer Information for Components
GUI LOOKUP ACAD_IN_USE_BLOCK_LAYER_INFO_ACAD_2 <Unused>,no 
# ============================================================================
# Indicate whether we want to store the insert location for the block reference
