ACAD_2_STORE_INSERT_POINT "$(ACAD_IN_STORE_INSERT_POINT_ACAD_2)"
GUI OPTIONAL CHECKBOX_WITHLABEL ACAD_IN_STORE_INSERT_POINT_ACAD_2 yes%no Store Insert Location on Components
